One specimen (
<emphasis id="4095EAFE247BBD22FEDFDD231919A07A" box="[383,550,865,891]" italics="true" pageId="101" pageNumber="102">Galeano 2080</emphasis>
) has larger leaves and exceptionally large fruits (
<quantity id="B5199B09247BBD22FBC9DD231FF6A07A" box="[1129,1225,865,891]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.33" pageId="101" pageNumber="102" unit="cm" value="13.3">13.3 cm</quantity>
